Get path to padlocdev example

Source: R/example.R
padlocdev_example.Rd

padlocdev comes bundled with a number of sample files in its inst/extdata directory. This function make them easy to access.

Usage

padlocdev_example(file = NULL)

Arguments

file

Name of file. If NULL, the example files will be listed.

Value

A base::character().

Examples

padlocdev_example()
